QuestData.Title: Looting the Looters
QuestData.Description:
<The Mawsworn was carrying a Korthian artifact.
It's unclear what the enemy wants with such relics, but you suspect the attendants in Keeper's Respite would want to see them returned.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve $1oa Korthian Artifacts from the Mawsworn.
QuestData.RewardText: Now this is special. This implement is used by the Fatescribe in his work.
